= IMG_SaveJPG =

Save a SDL_Surface into a JPEG image file.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int IMG_SaveJPG(SDL_Surface *surface, const char *file, int quality);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''surface'''
|SDL surface to save
|-
|'''file'''
|file name
|-
|'''quality'''
|[0; 33] is Lowest quality, [34; 66] is Middle quality, [67; 100] is Highest quality
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0 if successful, -1 on error

